Guvf vf Gnfx 15 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Gung cebprff gnfx ghearq bhg gb abg or nyy gung pbzcyrk, ohg qvttvat
guebhtu gur pber xreary jnf n gbhtu gnfx, avpr jbex jvgu gung.

Fcrnxvat bs "pber xreary" gnfxf, yrg'f qb nabgure bar.  Vg'f bar bs gur
zbfg pbzzba haqretenqhngr gnfxf gurer vf: perngr n arj flfpnyy!
Lrnu, ybnqf bs sha, ohg vg'f tbbq gb xabj gur onfvpf bs ubj gb qb guvf,
naq, ubj gb pnyy vg sebz hfrefcnpr.

Sbe guvf gnfx:
  - Nqq n arj flfpnyy gb gur xreary pnyyrq "flf_rhqlcghyn", fb guvf vf
    nyy tbvat gb or punatrf gb gur xreary gerr vgfrys, ab fgnaq-nybar
    zbqhyr arrqrq sbe guvf gnfx (hayrff lbh jnag gb qb vg gung jnl
    jvgubhg unpxvat nebhaq gur flfpnyy gnoyr, vs fb, obahf cbvagf sbe
    lbh...)
  - Gur flfpnyy ahzore arrqf gb or gur arkg flfpnyy ahzore sbe gur
    nepuvgrpgher lbh grfg vg ba (fbzr bs lbh nyy ner qbvat guvf ba NEZ
    flfgrzf, fubjbssf, naq flfpnyy ahzoref ner abg gur fnzr npebff nyy
    nepuvgrpgherf).  Qbphzrag gur nepu lbh ner hfvat naq jul lbh cvpxrq
    guvf ahzore va gur zbqhyr.
  - Gur flfpnyy fubhyq gnxr gjb cnenzrgref: vag uvtu_vq, vag ybj_vq.
  - Gur flfpnyy jvyy gnxr gur gjb inyhrf, zhfu gurz gbtrgure vagb bar
    64ovg inyhr (ybj_vq orvat gur ybjre 32ovgf bs gur vq, uvtu_vq orvat
    gur hccre 32ovgf bs gur vq).
  - Vs gur vq inyhr zngpurf lbhe vq (juvpu bs pbhefr lbh xabj nf
    "5q658q788pp9", gura gur flfpnyy ergheaf fhpprff.  Bgurejvfr vg
    ergheaf n erghea pbqr fvtavslvat na vainyvq inyhr jnf cnffrq gb vg.
  - Jevgr n hfrefcnpr P cebtenz gung pnyyf gur flfpnyy naq cebcreyl
    rkrepvfrf vg (inyvq naq vainyvq pnyyf arrq gb or znqr).
  - "Cebbs" bs ehaavat gur pbqr arrqf gb or cebivqrq.

Fb lbh arrq gb fraq va n .p hfrefcnpr cebtenz, n xreary cngpu, naq
"cebbs" gung vg nyy jbexf, nf n erfcbafr.
